	<div style="text-align:right;">
		RIBEIRO, Rhaysa Tomaschewsky<sup>1</sup>; MAZUR, Rui Fernando<sup>2</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa PUCPR-PIBIC		<BR>
